{"id": "1491986262972694558", "channel_id": "1433513650299076780", "type": 19, "author_id": "769372452580229131", "author_name": "kinbote.", "author_bot": false, "content": "No worries. You seem like you have a fair variety of limiteds so when you get to dtide (endgame) you should have a fair amount of choices in teams to build. \n\nCurrent limited banners are a bit hit or miss. Tulu and wanda are not very strong. Salvador is ok. Kathigura is strong but only at e3 and very weak before that. Half anni is coming up very soon so unless kath appeals to you it might make sense to save for that. Will likely get more banner variety then.", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T02:20:44.857000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["256248182898556928"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1491984620550361108", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
